Manchester United's English striker Mason Greenwood JOHANNESBURG - Manchester United’s Mason Greenwood is trending on social media for all the wrong reasons. This after his girlfriend, Harriet Robson, accused the Red Devil star of physical abuse. In several posts on her official Instagram account, Robson posted snapshots and a video of the bruises. READ: Mbuso Mandela video admitting to abuse goes viral Reports suggest the club have been made aware of the Greenwood allegations. The police were also notified. Greenwood could be suspended pending the police investigation.